title: Osho_The Last Testament Vol-1 #8_why are you so attractive.mp4
description:
Better quality video.Length 1 hour, 43 min. 

The Last Testament, Vol 1, Chapter #08
Chapter title: Commune Is The Way
25 July 1985 pm in Jesus Grove, US

Denise Kovacevic, KATU TV, CHANNEL 2
PORTLANDS, OREGON, US

Q: PROBABLY THE FIRST QUESTION ON MY MIND IS, WHAT IS IT ABOUT YOU, WHAT IS IT ABOUT YOUR RELIGION, THAT PEOPLE FIND SO APPEALING? WE SEE PEOPLE LIKE ISABEL AND SHEELA AND SARITA AND K.D., PEOPLE THAT WE THINK ARE LIKE OURSELVES, AND SEE WHAT THEY HAVE HERE, AND WE ASK OURSELVES, WHAT IS IT ABOUT YOU AND THIS PLACE THAT IS SO ATTRACTIVE TO PEOPLE?

A: It is very simple. I am so ordinary a man that nobody can feel any inferiority with me. ....
..............................
Osho was dancing with Denise, journalist and Vivek at the end..very joyful moments
